  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies arguments for creating or cloning a typeface with specific variation settings and palette overrides.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKFontArguments` is a ref struct that holds parameters for selecting a font from a collection, configuring variation design positions, and overriding palette colors. Pass it to <xref:SkiaSharp.SKTypeface.Clone*> to create a typeface variant.

## Examples

```csharp
var args = new SKFontArguments
{
    CollectionIndex = 0,
    PaletteIndex = 1
};
var variant = typeface.Clone(args);
```
]]></format></remarks>
